            <div type="transcript" id="J428">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Taking up the fair Ideal,</l>
                    <l>Just to cast her down</l>
                    <l>When a fracture -- we discover --</l>
                    <l>Or a splintered Crown --</l>
                    <l>Makes the Heavens portable --</l>
                    <l>And the Gods -- a lie --</l>
                    <l>Doubtless -- "Adam" -- scowled at Eden --</l>
                    <l>For his perjury!</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Cherishing -- our poor Ideal --</l>
                    <l>Till in purer dress --</l>
                    <l>We behold her -- glorified --</l>
                    <l>Comforts -- search -- like this --</l>
                    <l>Till the broken creatures --</l>
                    <l>We adored -- for whole --</l>
                    <l>Stains -- all washed --</l>
                    <l>Transfigured -- mended --</l>
                    <l>Meet us -- with a smile --</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
